      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d076n1-ptr" id="PJA03d076n1">1</a>
      
   <p>From Alexander Popes Satires of Dr. John Donne, Dean of St. Pauls, Versified, Satire IV, l. 186187.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d076n2-ptr" id="PJA03d076n2">2</a>
      
   <p>The day on which <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> began his return to Philadelphia, 28 Aug.</p>

